<view class="exchangepage">
  <NavbarModel page-name="优惠券兑换" show-nav="{{true}}" icon-color="#fff" textColor="#fff" bgColor="#DC3A36" />

  <view class="exchange_header" style="margin-top:{{navHeight-1}}px">
    <image class="headerImg" src="../../images/dhcode.png"></image>
  </view>


  <view class="title">
    优惠券兑换 </view>
  <!-- 输入框 -->
  <view class="exchang_input">
    <input class="input" type="text" placeholder="请输入兑换码" value="{{inputValue}}" bindinput="bindcodeInput" />
    <!-- <van-icon name="scan" size="20" bindtap="scanCode"/> -->
  </view>

  <view class="button_">
    <van-button color="#D13127" block disabled="{{disabled}}" bind:click="exchangeCoupon">确认兑换 </van-button>
  </view>

  <!-- 介绍 -->
  <view class="content">
    <view class="c_title">
      兑换说明
    </view>
    <view class="text">
      1.兑换码只能兑换一次，并在有效期内兑换.
    </view>
    <view class="text">
      2.自动识别兑换成相应的优惠券和年卡3兑换的产品不支持退款，只能用于消费.
    </view>
    <view class="text">
      3.最终解释权我们所有.
    </view>

  </view>
</view>